OL,5, A horse owner has spoken of his        
OL,6, devastation after a car crashed into   
OL,7, his trailer, resulting in the death of 
OL,8, his two five-month-old foals.          
OL,10,FJames Mason, from near Market          
OL,11,FHarborough in Leicestershire, was      
OL,12,Ftravelling on the M25 near Enfield when
OL,13,Fa car clipped the back of his horsebox.
OL,15,FThe trailer flipped and crashed,       
OL,16,Fkilling one foal, with the other having
OL,17,Fto be put down due to its injuries.    
OL,19,FMr Mason said: "I'm heartbroken... I   
OL,20,Fjust want the driver to come forward." 
